made us laugh.
l…

Lilly Bernal Pino as Monica de Armas

Luis Bofill as Guillermo Bahos

It’s time to come home. Watch the premiere of FX’s Mayans 5.24 on FX. Stream on Hulu.

Elgin James is a force for growth, creativity, empowerment and exploration, a poet, an artist, a leader, a true auteur, a person of his word, funny as hell and, thankfully, a friend.
Forever grateful. Hoping good fortune continues to bring us together. @mayansfx 
#ElginJames #MayansMC

It was my great good fortune to direct Mayans MC, Episode 503, beautifully written by Vivian Tse (#WGA) and brought to life by our exceptional ensemble and inspired crew. Will forever be in Elgin James’ debt for encouraging, trusting and guiding me. Thank you for helping all of us discover things inside of ourselves over the last 5 seasons. 

Appreciate you, our Mayans fandom, for riding with us and for your support throughout. Grateful for the response to all of our work. Can’t wait for you to see what lies ahead in S5!

Congratulations to @jdpardo for directing last night’s episode. 
Grateful for your leadership, artistry and hard work. You gave everything you had over the last five seasons, and kept coming back for more. Thank you for setting the bar so high. Abrazo fuerte. #MayansMC

@UniondeReyesFilm our short, is an official selection of the @HollyShorts Film Festival. We are excited to be part of a festival that supports the members of @SAGAFTRA, @WGA and our industry at large. Please join us for our World Premiere, Thursday, August 17, @2:30, @ChineseTheatres in Hollywood, CA. Nos veremos allí, familia. With music by @PinoGrillo.music, here’s our trailer:

We met in an acting class in Junior High School, did plays throughout High School and College…and now the world will know what I’ve known: your depth, intelligence, artistry and courage are inspirational. It took some convincing, but thank you for playing “Monica” and allowing me to work with my favorite scene partner, again, @lillypinopublic. Grateful for your work as an actor and producer on our film @uniondereyesfilm. Thank you @hollyshorts for a fantastic World Premiere. 

Appreciate @joseffofhollywood_official for putting some Hollywood history on Lilly’s wrist. Lucille Ball. I Love Lilly.

Strike on!

Thank you to the cast and crew of @UniondeReyesFilm for making our film a reality and for making our World Premiere @hollyshorts an unforgettable celebration of collaboration, synergy, passion, creativity, resourcefulness and hard work. Los felicito, familia.

Andre Braugher was an actor’s actor. On the set of SVU, I walked onto an unlit set adjacent to the bullpen set we were shooting on. I wanted to run the lines for the scene I was about to shoot with one of my idols, Andre Braugher. Surprisingly, he was in the shadows, humming a cadence that seemed familiar to me. Was it song? A poem? A sonnet? No, it was the rhythm of our scene. He was feeling the music, the cadence of our scene. Like a conductor before an orchestra, he revealed the scene to me without words. Some artists are on another level. It was my great good fortune. Rest easy.
